snippet.title: BBC
snippet.description:
The BBC is the world’s leading public service broadcaster.

We’re impartial and independent, and every day we create distinctive, world-class programmes and content which inform, educate and entertain millions of people in the UK and around the world.

SUBSCRIBE to our YouTube channel to get the best of BBC entertainment and comedy programmes, stories from science and nature documentaries, and much more! 👉 https://bit.ly/2IXqEIn

Get ALL your fresh TV, and sofa-hugging box sets on BBC iPlayer 👉 https://bbc.in/2J18jYJ
